data.description: Charming Colonial home circa 1890 on a wide yard.  The room fit young, the porch is restored and there is a classic wood exterior.  Traditional floor plan with a big bright living room, formal dining room, and a new first floor laundry room.  Original moldings, woodwork, and a grand staircase.  Big kitchen loaded with cabinets and an island work space.  Four big bedrooms with abundant with closets and visible wood floors.  Optional 5th bedroom or office. 1.5 bathrooms.  Brand new Furnace and Central Air Conditioning.  Brand new Tankless hot water tank and newly insulated basement.  Brand new flooring in the dining room.
